result.name: Ki’s Roasted Goose Restaurant

reviews.text: Roast pork was really nice. Vegetables boiled just nice. Soup was delicious.
A very good value place for quality hk style roasted goose. Fast food environment
Good food and good coffee. Yet there's room for improvement in terms of hygienics.
Delicious goose slices with rice! It is deboned!!

The scrambled eggs is to die for! Had toast, eggs, noodles, roasted duck, char siew and was super  happy with the meal. Quick and friendly service, which is rare in Hong Kong. Dishes can be a little heavy on the salty side but I'll still recommend the place. Happy to revisit.
